* TA,) in this and all the following senses. (TA.) ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A cleft in a mountain, to which birds"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlT~ayoru","text_ar":"الطَّيْرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", for which"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlmaTaru","text_ar":"المَطَرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is erroneously substituted in [several of] the copies of the K, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"resort:"},{"kind":"text","text":"pl. as above. (K, TA.) ―         -b4-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A branch"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a tree, (S, A, * Mgh, * Msb, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"growing out a part,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"divaricating,"},{"kind":"text","text":"therefrom: (Msb, * TA:) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"extremity of a branch:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA: [said in the latter to be tropical in this latter sense; but why, I see not:]) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$uEabN","text_ar":"شُعَبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Mgh, Msb, TA) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$iEaAbN","text_ar":"شِعَابٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", as above. (TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$uEabu AlguSoni","text_ar":"شُعَبُ الغُصْنِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The divaricating,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"straggling,"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"branchlets,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"extremities"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"shoots"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"stalks"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the branch."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And [hence]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaSFA fiY raA^osihaA $uEobataAni","text_ar":"عَصًا فِى رَاْسِهَا شُعْبَتَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A staff having at his head two forking portions"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"projections"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; (A, TA;) and Az mentions, as heard by him from the Arabs, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$uEobaAni","text_ar":"شُعْبَانِ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", without"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"t","text_ar":"ت"},{"kind":"text","text":", instead of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$uEobataAni","text_ar":"شُعْبَتَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in this phrase. (L, TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$uEobapN mino rayoHaAnK","text_ar":"شُعْبَةٌ مِنْ رَيْحَانٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A sprig, spray, bunch,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"branchlet, of sweet basil,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of sweet-smelling plants"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$uEobapN mino $aEarK","text_ar":"شُعْبَةٌ مِنْ شَعَرٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mino SuwfK","text_ar":"مِنْ صُوفٍ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A lock,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"flock, of hair"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of wool"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (JK in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Twq","text_ar":"طوق"},{"kind":"text","text":".) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^anaA $uEobapN mino dawoHatika","text_ar":"اَنَا شُعْبَةٌ مِنْ دَوْحَتِكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I am a branch,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"branchlet, of thy great tree"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A, TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"masoA^alapN kaviyrapu Al$~uEabi","text_ar":"مَسْاَلَةٌ كَثِيرَةُ الشُّعَبِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A question having many branches,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ramifications"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Msb.) And [the pl.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$uEabN","text_ar":"شُعَبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[as meaning] (tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fingers:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA:) one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qabaDa Ealayohi bi$uEabi yadihi","text_ar":"قَبَضَ عَلَيْهِ بِشُعَبِ يَدِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He laid hold upon it with his fingers."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaEada bayona $uEobatayohaA","text_ar":"قَعَدَ بَيْنَ شُعْبَتَيْهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He sat between her two legs:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bayona $uEabihaA AlA^arobaEi","text_ar":"بَيْنَ شُعَبِهَا الاَرْبَعِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  [He sat (in the Mgh"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaEada","text_ar":"قَعَدَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", as implied in the A, and in the Msb"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jalasa","text_ar":"جَلَسَ"},{"kind":"text","text":",)]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"between her arms and her legs;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, Mgh, Msb, K;) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"between her legs and the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$uforaAni","text_ar":"شُفْرَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[dual of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$uforN","text_ar":"شُفْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v.,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of her"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faroj","text_ar":"فَرْج"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (A, Mgh, K;) occurring in a trad.; (Mgh, Msb;) an allusion to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jimaAE","text_ar":"جِمَاع"},{"kind":"text","text":". (A, Mgh, Msb, K.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$uEobataA Alr~aHoli","text_ar":"شُعْبَتَا الرَّحْلِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aroxaAni","text_ar":"شَرْخَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"two upright pieces of wood"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the"},{"kind":"page_break","n":1557},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"camel's saddle; its"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaAdimap","text_ar":"قَادِمَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"and its"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A=xirah","text_ar":"ا=خِرَه"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Mgh.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aigorizi All~aHoma fiY $uEabi Als~af~uwdi","text_ar":"اِغْرِزِ اللَّحْمَ فِى شُعَبِ السَّفُّودِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Infix thou the flesh-meat upon the prongs of the roastinginstrument"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A, TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$uEobapu minojalK","text_ar":"شُعْبَةُ مِنْجَلٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A tooth of a reaping-hook"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (K in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sn","text_ar":"سن"},{"kind":"text","text":".) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$uEobapN mino $uEabi Als~iyni","text_ar":"شُعْبَةٌ مِنْ شُعَبِ السِّينِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A tooth,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cusp, of the teeth,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cusps, of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"s","text_ar":"س"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$uEab","text_ar":"شُعَب"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"s","text_ar":"س"},{"kind":"text","text":"being three. (S and L in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"s","text_ar":"س"},{"kind":"text","text":".) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$uEabu","text_ar":"شُعَبُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alfarasi","text_ar":"الفَرَسِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The outer parts,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"regions, of the horse"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aqoTaAruhu","text_ar":"اَقْطَارُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", A, or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nawaAHiyhi","text_ar":"نَوَاحِيهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", K);"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"all of them:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the prominent parts"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of them,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of him;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, and so in some copies of the K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"as the neck, and the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"minosaj","text_ar":"مِنْسَج"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"withers,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.], (S, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and the crests of the hips,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"such as his head, and his"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaArik","text_ar":"حَارِك"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"withers,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.],"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and the crests of his hips."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A.) ―         -b5-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A small water-course,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"channel in which water flows;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as in the phrase"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$uEobapN HaAfilN","text_ar":"شُعْبَةٌ حَافِلٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a small water-course filled with a torrent:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a water-course in sand;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K;) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the elevated part of a depressed tract into which sand has poured and remained."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A small portion of a"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"water-course such as is called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taloEap","text_ar":"تَلْعَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"; or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"what is smaller than a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taloEap","text_ar":"تَلْعَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"; accord. to different copies of the K;"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Al$~uEobapu","text_ar":"الشُّعْبَةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"being expl. as meaning"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA Sagura mina Alt~aloEapi","text_ar":"مَا صَغُرَ مِنَ التَّلْعَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and, in one copy,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eani Alt~aloEapi","text_ar":"عَنِ التَّلْعَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such as is large, of the channels for irrigation of valleys:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA:) or, as some say,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a branch from a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taloEap","text_ar":"تَلْعَة"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from a valley,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"torrent-bed, taking a different course therefrom:"},{"kind":"text","text":"pl. as above. (TA.) ―         -b6-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A portion, part,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"piece,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a thing; or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"somewhat"},{"kind":"text","text":"thereof: (S, Msb, K, TA:) pl. as above. (TA.) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ai$oEabo liY $uEobapF mina AlmaAli","text_ar":"اِشْعَبْ لِى شُعْبَةً مِنَ المَالِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Give thou to me a portion of the property."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY yadihi $uEobapu xayorK","text_ar":"فِى يَدِهِ شُعْبَةُ خَيْرٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"In his hand is somewhat of good,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of wealth"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) And it is said in a trad.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlHayaA='u $uEobapN mina AlA_iymaAni","text_ar":"الحَيَا=ءُ شُعْبَةٌ مِنَ الاـِيمَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Modesty is a part of faith:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and in another,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Al$~abaAbu $uEobapN mina","text_ar":"الشَّبَابُ شُعْبَةٌ مِنَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aljunuwni","text_ar":"الجُنُونِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Youth is a part of insanity"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) In explanation of the phrase, in the Kur [lxxvii. 30],"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_ilaY Zil~K *iY valaAvi $uEabK","text_ar":"اـِلَى ظِلٍّ ذِى ثَلَاثِ شُعَبٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Unto a shade,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"shadow, having three parts,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"divisions"},{"kind":"text","text":"], it is said that the fire [of Hell], on the day of resurrection, will divide into three parts; and whenever they shall attempt to go forth to a place, it will repel them: by"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Zil~","text_ar":"ظِلّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"being here meant that the fire will form a covering; for [literally] there will be no"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Zil~","text_ar":"ظِلّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in this case. (Th, L.) ―         -b7-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A piece such as is called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ruw^bap","text_ar":"رُوبَة"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with which a wooden bowl"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"is repaired."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S.) ―         -b8-  Accord. to Lth, (T, TA,)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$uEabu Ald~ahori","text_ar":"شُعَبُ الدَّهْرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"means (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The changes,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"vicissitudes, of time"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fortune;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, A, TA;) and he cites the saying of Dhu-r-Rummeh,"},{"kind":"quote","text":"walaA tuqas~imu $aEobFA waAHidFA $uEabu"},{"kind":"text","text":"which he explains by saying, i. e. I thought that one thing, or state of things, would not be divided into many things, or states: [i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Nor"},{"kind":"text","text":"did I think that the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"vicissitudes"},{"kind":"text","text":"of fortune would"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"divide one whole body of men"},{"kind":"text","text":"into many parties:] but Az disapproves of this explanation, and says that"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$uEab","text_ar":"شُعَب"},{"kind":"text","text":"here means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Intentions, designs,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"purposes:"},{"kind":"text","text":"he says that the poet describes tribes assembled together in the [season called]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rabiyE","text_ar":"رَبِيع"},{"kind":"text","text":", who, when they desired to return to the watering-places, differed in their intentions, or designs; wherefore he says,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Nor"},{"kind":"text","text":"did I think that various"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"intentions"},{"kind":"text","text":"would"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"divide"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"one whole body of men"},{"kind":"text","text":"who before had] a consentient intention. (L, TA.) ―         -b9-  [See also the pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$iEaAbN","text_ar":"شِعَابٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"below.]"}],"source_refs":["K","S","Mgh","Msb","TA","A","T"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}